作业之三：说一说 .retain_grad() 和 .backward(retain_graph=True) 的作用¶

.retain_grad()：决定非叶子节点能不能存梯度¶

.backward(retain_graph=True)：决定能不能传梯度，直有能穿梯度才能存梯度¶

作业之四：说一说 .data 和 .detach() 的联系¶

data和datach的共同点：¶

  Tensor
  require s_gradFalse
In [81]:
import torch

a = torch.tensor([[2.]],requires_grad = True)
print('a',a)
print('*'*60)
a_data = a.data
a_data[:] = 6
print('a_dataa',a)
print('*'*60)
print('a_datarequires_grad',a_data.requires_grad)

a tensor([[2.]], requires_grad=True)

a_dataa tensor([[6.]], requires_grad=True)

import torch

a = torch.tensor([[2.]],requires_grad = True)
print('a',a)
print('*'*60)
a_data = a.detach()
a_data[:] = 6
print('detacha',a)
print('*'*60)
print('a_detachrequires_grad',a_data.requires_grad)

a tensor([[2.]], requires_grad=True)
************************************************************
detacha tensor([[6.]], requires_grad=True)
************************************************************
a_detachrequires_grad False

data和datach的不同点：¶

  datadetach
  data      detach

data:此时就会产生错误的梯度¶

In [127]:
a = torch.FloatTensor([[1., 2.]])
b = torch.FloatTensor([[3.], [4.]])
d = torch.FloatTensor([5.])
b.requires_grad = True
d.requires_grad = True
c = torch.matmul(a, b)
# c_ = c.detach()
c_ = c.data
f = torch.matmul(d, c)
c_[:] = 1
f.backward()

d.grad

正确的梯度应该是 11¶
